VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \.execute\(\s*f[\'\"]|\.execute\(\s*[^\)]*%\s*\(|raw\(\s*f[\'\"]
WHEN EXPR MISSING:paramstyle|cursor\.execute\s*\(.*%s.*,|bindparams|params=
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects likely string-built SQL execution in framework data access paths.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Flask SQL Injection Sink.
